ypes);\\n                }\\n            });\\n        }\\n        catch (DateTimeException exc)\\n        {\\n            return false;\\n        }\\n    }\\n\\n    private static boolean isAllowed(TemporalType needle, TemporalType... allowed)\\n    {\\n        for (TemporalType t : allowed)\\n        {\\n            if (t.equals(needle))\\n            {\\n                return true;\\n            }\\n        }\\n        return false;\\n    }\\n}\\n\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1777526095237}}\n1695:[recv] {\"type\": \"turn_end\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"toolCall\", \"id\": \"call_yUlChqhOYR6yqnydUcbkUTkJ|fc_0dc41ea7c44432300169f2e54ed304819583a08819b2c07b3c\", \"name\": \"read\", \"arguments\": {\"path\": \"/home/jovan/Work/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/source_context/com.ethlo.time/itu/1.10.3/main/extracted/com/ethlo/time/ITU.java\"}, \"partialJson\": \"{\\\"path\\\":\\\"/home/jovan/Work/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/source_context/com.ethlo.time/itu/1.10.3/main/extracted/com/ethlo/time/ITU.java\\\"}\"}, {\"type\": \"toolCall\", \"id\": \"call_tahywvcdaXuvIoHPySyWGRqd|fc_0dc41ea7c44432300169f2e54ed318819589883b0be91476b4\", \"name\": \"read\", \"arguments\": {\"path\": \"/home/jovan/Work/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/source_context/com.ethlo.time/itu/1.10.3/main/extracted/com/ethlo/time/ParseConfig.java\"}, \"partialJson\": \"{\\\"path\\\":\\\"/home/jovan/Work/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/source_context/com.ethlo.time/itu/1.10.3/main/extracted/com/ethlo/time/ParseConfig.java\\\"}\"}, {\"type\": \"toolCall\", \"id\": \"call_GT62YjDL2EylPVMbLWTdEEn8|fc_0dc41ea7c44432300169f2e54ed32081958c7bc4dc46fe6312\", \"name\": \"read\", \"arguments\": {\"path\": \"/home/jovan/Work/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/source_context/com.ethlo.time/itu/1.10.3/main/extracted/com/ethlo/time/internal/fixed/ITUPa